<lb n="0031a21"/><head type="no">No. 1204</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0031a22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0031009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保二十年刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】東寺三密藏古寫本</note>聖無動尊一字出生八大童子祕
<lb n="0031a23"/>要法品</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0031a24"/>
<lb n="0031a25"/><byline type="Translator">大興善寺翻經院述</byline>
<lb n="0031a26"/><p>金剛手言。一切眾生意想不同。或順或逆。是
<lb n="0031a27"/>故如來現慈怒身。隨作利益。解云。諸佛大悲
<lb n="0031a28"/>愍眾生故。即<note n="0031010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝捨【乙】＊</note><app n="0031010"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">捨</rdg></app>順者以順而勸。若<app type="＊" source="0031010"><lem>於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">捨</rdg></app>逆者
<lb n="0031a29"/>以逆而制也。一佛住忿怒三昧。時十方諸佛
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1204.0031b" n="0031b"/>
<lb n="0031b01"/>同共入忿怒瞋三昧。豈毘盧遮那於無相中
<lb n="0031b02"/>示現明王。時諸佛菩薩更不現忿怒身哉。是
<lb n="0031b03"/>故四方如來。現教令身降伏<note n="0031011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＋（生）【乙】</note><app n="0031011"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">眾生</rdg></app>魔。雖然猶不
<lb n="0031b04"/>親隨逐。所以本誓不同。或降三世菩薩。降伏
<lb n="0031b05"/>天魔及三世貪瞋癡。或軍荼利菩薩調伏常
<lb n="0031b06"/>隨魔。謂毘那夜迦。及人魔或焰魔特迦。降
<lb n="0031b07"/>伏龍魔及諸怨敵。或金剛夜叉。調伏鬼魔及
<lb n="0031b08"/>無智者。如是種種不可具說。不動明王&M010527;隨
<lb n="0031b09"/>行者。若天<note n="0031012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031012"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>毘那夜迦。若龍若鬼。所作障
<lb n="0031b10"/>礙一時消滅。然諸佛菩薩。若同住一三昧者。
<lb n="0031b11"/>可有隨不動弘誓之使者。<note n="0031013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爰＝受【甲】</note><app n="0031013"><lem>爰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app><note n="0031014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＋（中）【乙】</note><app n="0031014"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">有中</rdg></app>三藏不空
<lb n="0031b12"/>能達明道。即披見祕藏要文。有不動明<note n="0031015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031015"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一
<lb n="0031b13"/>字心密語。即以八字而嚴一字。其八字者即
<lb n="0031b14"/>歸命<note n="0031016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋句【甲】</note><app n="0031016"><lem>句</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以句</rdg></app>也。<tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E045;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唅〕－【乙】＊</note><app n="0031017"><lem>唅</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt>字為本尊。若爾寧上八字
<lb n="0031b15"/>無其形哉。所以者何。<tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔那〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031018"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt><tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔莫〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031019"><lem>莫</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt>等八字。一
<lb n="0031b16"/>一皆歸敬於<tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E045;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0031017"><lem>唅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt>之一字。是故從其八字出
<lb n="0031b17"/>生歸敬使者。圍繞於<tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E045;</t><t lang="chi"><app type="＊" source="0031017"><lem>唅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt>之本尊。所以有
<lb n="0031b18"/>八大童子。一慧光菩薩<note place="inline">金剛云。迴光即以慧如<note n="0031020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔光〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031020"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>照迴一切故</note>。二慧
<lb n="0031b19"/>喜菩薩<note place="inline">金剛云。<note n="0031021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慧＝迴【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0031021"><lem>慧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">迴</rdg></app>喜即迴慧為喜</note>。三阿耨達菩薩。四指德
<lb n="0031b20"/>菩薩。五烏俱婆&CB00344;。六清淨比丘。七矜羯羅。八
<lb n="0031b21"/>制吒迦。是等使者四智四波羅<note n="0031022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【乙】＊</note><app n="0031022"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>。為親隨
<lb n="0031b22"/>順大日教令故。顯現此形圍繞聖無動尊也。
<lb n="0031b23"/>各別真言中顯示其義。解云。東方金剛部。即
<lb n="0031b24"/>菩提心門。以日光為喻。所以出生使者名慧
<lb n="0031b25"/>光。南方寶部即福德門。所以出生使者名慧
<lb n="0031b26"/>喜。以福智二嚴為喜故。西方蓮華部即智慧
<lb n="0031b27"/>門。所以出<note n="0031023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝生【乙】</note><app n="0031023"><lem>現</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>使者名阿耨達。此云無熱。表
<lb n="0031b28"/>蓮華生池水而清淨無垢故。北方羯磨部即
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1204.0031c" n="0031c"/>
<lb n="0031c01"/>精進門。所以出生使者名指德也。今此部指
<lb n="0031c02"/>前三部德。即依精進能得果故。所以名指德
<lb n="0031c03"/><note place="inline">已上四智</note>金剛波羅<app type="＊" source="0031022"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">密</rdg></app>即菩提心行。所以出現。使
<lb n="0031c04"/>者名烏俱<note n="0031024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝波【甲】</note><app n="0031024"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">波</rdg></app>&CB00344;。此云超越住世也。寶波羅
<lb n="0031c05"/><app type="＊" source="0031022"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">密</rdg></app>福德心行。所以出生使者名清淨比丘。
<lb n="0031c06"/><note n="0031025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔表比丘〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031025"><lem>表比丘</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>能守護法寶故。法波羅<app type="＊" source="0031022"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">密</rdg></app>慈悲心
<lb n="0031c07"/>行。所以出現使者名矜羯羅。此云隨順。業波
<lb n="0031c08"/>羅<app type="＊" source="0031022"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">密</rdg></app>即方便心行。所以出生使者名制<note n="0031026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝吒【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0031026"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031c09"/>迦。此云息災也。菩薩方便現瞋形故也。八童
<lb n="0031c10"/>子所依說已<note n="0031027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竟＝畢【乙】</note><app n="0031027"><lem>竟</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">畢</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0031c11"/><p>若行者欲得現當悉地者。行法之中稱彼各
<lb n="0031c12"/>名。請乞救護及結印誦&CB00057;。即成一切世間殊
<lb n="0031c13"/>勝悉地</p>
<lb n="0031c14"/><p>慧光童子菩薩真言<note n="0031028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0031028"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0031029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝印【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0031029"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">印</rdg></app>金剛合掌忍願合如針</note></p>
<lb n="0031c15"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0031030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲乙二本俱梵字總無之</note>&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【乙】＊</note><app n="0031031"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日<note n="0031032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【乙】＊</note><app n="0031032"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app></zi><sg>二合</sg></yin><note place="inline">一</note></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi">帝</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E04A;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>入<note n="0031033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【乙】＊</note><app n="0031033"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app></zi><sg><note n="0031034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0031034"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64A;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00256;二〕－【甲】，&CB00256;＝羅【乙】</note><app n="0031035"><lem>&CB00256;<note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">羅二</rdg></app></t></tt>
<lb n="0031c16"/>
<lb n="0031c17"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65E;</t><t lang="chi">菩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi">地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47E;</t><t lang="chi">質</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CF55;</t><t lang="chi">多<note n="0031036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【乙】＊</note><app n="0031036"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt>
<lb n="0031c18"/><note n="0031037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歸命本尊四字乙本作本文下同</note><note n="0031037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（歸命本尊）四字夾註＝（歸命本尊）四字本文【乙】下同</note><app n="0031037"><lem><note place="inline">歸命本尊</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">歸命本尊</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0031c19"/><p>慧喜菩薩真言曰<note place="inline">金合忍願如寶形</note></p>
<lb n="0031c20"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B448;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>怛曩</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin><note place="inline">一</note></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi">帝</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">娑</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0C1;</t><t lang="chi">度<note place="inline">二</note></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">訶</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt>
<lb n="0031c21"/>
<lb n="0031c22"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A54D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0031038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抳＝尼【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0031038"><lem>抳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">尼</rdg></app><note place="inline">三</note></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi">莫<note place="inline">歸命本尊</note></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0031c23"/>
<lb n="0031c24"/><p>阿耨達菩薩真言<app type="＊" source="0031028"><lem>曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">金合忍願如蓮葉</note></p>
